column4: Great for you, maybe! I'm the one who has to fucking bear your child, you know!
I heard from my mom that childbirth is really fucking painful. How're you gonna make it up to me, huh?
I'll stay with you forever, how's that?
…I-Idiot. O-Of course you will. I'mma be the mother of your child, afterall.
Indeed, that's my baby inside your belly.
